#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: C/edit-style.page:8
msgid ""
"Styles control the overall appearance of the plots, including colors, fonts, "
"line widths, ticks, grid, and more. Graphs comes with a selection of built-"
"in styles to choose from, and you can create and edit your own to get "
"exactly the look you want."
msgstr ""
"Les styles définissent l’apparence générale des graphiques, dont les "
"couleurs, les polices, les largeurs de ligne, les graduations, la grille, et "
